{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01REwMwkwpsEgYsxuRXUuKS9","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspace/cmd/cloche/init.go:prompt=\"## Task: ${CLOCHE_TASK_TITLE}\n/workspace/cmd/cloche/init.go:${CLOCHE_TASK_BODY}\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:  step ready-tasks {\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    run     = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh 1\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:  ready-tasks:success -> prepare-prompt [\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_ID    = output[0].id,\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_TITLE = output[0].title,\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_BODY  = output[0].description\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:  ready-tasks:fail       -> abort\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_ID = output.task_id\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:The `ready-tasks` step outputs JSON; wire output mappings extract fields and inject\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:Environment variables (`CLOCHE_TASK_ID`, `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR`, etc.) are injected into\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:  step ready-tasks {\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    run     = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh 1\"\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:  ready-tasks:success -> prepare-prompt [\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_ID    = output[0].id,\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_TITLE = output[0].title,\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    CLOCHE_TASK_BODY  = output[0].description\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:  ready-tasks:fail       -> abort\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:  prepare-prompt:success -> develop [ CLOCHE_TASK_ID = output.task_id ]","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PBzqGrRSxSxC8pWZNjvguQ","session_id":"2f8bcbbf-b8aa-4f20-9779-dee3a5fa668b","uuid":"704525f2-f049-4c59-a85e-fb4b51200764"}
